Sorts an array of Player objects in order of their Elo rating (Player.getElo()), from highest to lowest.

Sorts an array of Player objects in order of their match Player.getWins(), from highest to lowest.
Tournament
Defines a bracket-style tournament that can handle any number of players by making use of byes.
